# Local development / CI reference only — never commit real values.
#
# Fly deploy secrets are loaded from Vault in CI (see .github/actions/vault-secrets).
# Bootstrap: bun run seed-fly-token --mint  →  .fly-token (gitignored)
# CI: gh secret set FLY_TOKEN --body "$(cat .fly-token)"
# Later: bun run seed-fly-token --vault
